      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/541183936_18367877323151991_5589791025306880089_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_s1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxMTIxMjI5NjMyNTM1OTEzMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=mWxVf1M_AhoQ7kNvwEKGsx7&amp;_nc_oc=Adqrka6XZv4o4x6tLmlfVUua9VinIwX3JZiH57c_DLlrEQ9mrb7cGfw3pXFS-2GRsNo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DKPXyLVrbxAlxENVrjHOjA&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_AfyD076xml42sj4BnE7CtxCF-5kzL6-Fw0ekf1fv02C7eQ&amp;oe=69CA3B69" alt="Slide 1 fra @peter_folkmar" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/541147075_18367877347151991_1732978557541008739_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_s1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxMTIxMjI5NjMxNjk2NTA1OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=qHXkADO-KrQQ7kNvwEN7qTW&amp;_nc_oc=AdrX3pRQq8dLaGNRSWRFYSKeRb1TeT108MdZaWKuM36SKhl0ADnPJKcX5Z9iDaZCEmQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DKPXyLVrbxAlxENVrjHOjA&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afzjh0-zYGxLnhwYhhKa4LwlhLPVknK4XkXpfWb9uOHEtg&amp;oe=69CA30AE" alt="Slide 2 fra @peter_folkmar" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/541153736_18367877464151991_7361586404826359651_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_s1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxMTIxMjI5NjM0MjEwMDQwNg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=ZL3YeimfQxkQ7kNvwHQVAwl&amp;_nc_oc=Ado5BOl6EZL-3HYIe1EzBsbUn3zbYK9lBjNwJ7XJPv7XcrilOLn7OmL9mpgn1obSdH4&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DKPXyLVrbxAlxENVrjHOjA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxWr3d5WTeA-MI28_5jQY48TToezj4wg55BnhDl1qmLsw&amp;oe=69CA2979" alt="Slide 3 fra @peter_folkmar" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/541520840_18367877473151991_5349938994800403944_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_s1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxMTIxMjI5NjMwODU1NjQ1Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=CU-cUQ_7c6YQ7kNvwGaIBU_&amp;_nc_oc=Adrvh4TchhkipiuQWtXU6x3Z8FtrIomOl6-xBE6_yEX7To30XSLsVqDLU8tINRWepmg&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=DKPXyLVrbxAlxENVrjHOjA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxCCk9D26eqwxqOgivR6ceWS1LX-wr9D5RcaljJ6M2YnA&amp;oe=69CA1531" alt="Slide 4 fra @peter_folkmar" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (15 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@peter_folkmar</strong></p><p>SMK THY, the new branch of the @smkmuseum in the northwestern part of Denmark is now reality. It’s taken nearly a decade to reach this point and what a journey it has been — for us, working in the museum, for all our new collaboration partners in the local municipality, for the architects, for the neighbours, and for everyone else that has been involved. The creation of the opening show has been a journey in itself: an exercise in rethinking the museum’s collection from a different perspective, and working from two locations across the country. A heartfelt thanks to the team behind the show for unrivaled devotion and professionalism without which we would never have obtained this result. It’s been intense and fun and wonderful to feel the team spirit and shared understanding of the significance of this undertaking. The result is truly a collective accomplishment. In the process, we all got Doverodde, the Limfjord, and the hills of Thy under our skin not to speak of its people. I’m sure everyone in our team agrees when I say that we are thrilled that the doors have finally opened and that we are able to share these gems in the museum’s collection and all the stories they entail with new audiences at this very special site in Denmark. The exhibition runs until November 2. Go go and enjoy! ☀️🌱 <br/>
 <br/>
#smkthy #statensmuseumforkunst #museumcollection #collectionhistory #rejsenfraparis #journeyfromparis #frenchart #modernism #thy #cultureandnature</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOA3_DUiC9q/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
